added: Shortly after Joe Biden's victory against Donald Trump in the 2020 presidential election, Malliotakis refused to acknowledge Biden's win, echoing Trump's refusal to concede the election.<ref>{{Cite web|last=Michel|first=Clifford|date=2020-11-10|title=Staten Island’s Malliotakis Echoes Trump’s Refusal to Admit Biden Won Election|url=https://www.thecity.nyc/2020/11/10/21559680/malliotakis-trump-loss-biden-win-aoc-staten-island|url-status=live|access-date=2021-02-19|website=[[The City (website)| THE CITY]]|language=en}}</ref>
